---

## 📖 About the Collection

**Whispers of the Soul** is a personal anthology of poems exploring the depths of emotion, nature, love, loss, and the surreal.  
Each piece is a whisper from a different corner of the human experience.

This collection is constantly evolving — like the thoughts that inspire it.

---

## 🌸 Categories

| Category         | Description                                           |
|------------------|-------------------------------------------------------|
| 🌿 **Nature**      | Quiet moments with wind, rain, trees, and time       |
| 💔 **Love & Loss** | Hearts that long, break, and heal                    |
| 🌌 **Abstract**     | Thoughtful wanderings, surreal or existential in tone |
| 🕊️ **Hope & Light** | Poems about healing, faith, and light returning      |

---

## 🌠 Featured Poem

> ### *Beneath the Moon*  
> _By [Your Name]_  
>
> The stars forgot to whisper back,  
> I spoke too loud in dreaming black.  
> But still I wait where shadows sing,  
> Beneath the hush of silver wing.

